_pRange.descriptionZh: 预定资源需要提前的时间数（例如预定火车票需在发车前至少一小时）
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The amount of time that is required between accepting the offer and the actual usage of the resource or service.
_pRange.rdfs:label: advanceBookingRequirement

_pRange.descriptionZh: 借款（或投资产生的）年度利率，以单一百分比数表示，表示贷款期间实际的年度资金成本。这包括与交易相关的任何费用或额外费用。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The annual rate that is charged for borrowing (or made by investing), expressed as a single percentage number that represents the actual yearly cost of funds over the term of a loan. This includes any fees or additional costs associated with the transaction.
_pRange.rdfs:label: annualPercentageRate

_pRange.descriptionZh: 通常指汽车后备箱的容积
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The available volume for cargo or luggage. For automobiles, this is usually the trunk volume.

Typical unit code(s): LTR for liters, FTQ for cubic foot/feet

Note: You can use minValue and maxValue to indicate ranges.
_pRange.rdfs:label: cargoVolume

_pRange.descriptionZh: 就是指收到订单和货物离开仓库或准备取件（如果是上门取货的话）之间的延迟。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The typical delay between the receipt of the order and the goods either leaving the warehouse or being prepared for pickup, in case the delivery method is on site pickup.
_pRange.rdfs:label: deliveryLeadTime

_pRange.descriptionZh: 该项的深度。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The depth of the item.
_pRange.rdfs:label: depth

_pRange.descriptionZh: 保修期限。一般的单位代码是ANN表示年数，MON表示月数，DAY表示天数。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The duration of the warranty promise. Common unitCode values are ANN for year, MON for months, or DAY for days.
_pRange.rdfs:label: durationOfWarranty

_pRange.descriptionZh: 报价的有效时间，例如促销折扣仅限于某一周有效。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The duration for which the given offer is valid.
_pRange.rdfs:label: eligibleDuration

_pRange.descriptionZh: 报价最多可有购买多少货品，例如每客户最多可以购买一个优惠产品。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The interval and unit of measurement of ordering quantities for which the offer or price specification is valid. This allows e.g. specifying that a certain freight charge is valid only for a certain quantity.
_pRange.rdfs:label: eligibleQuantity

_pRange.descriptionZh: 房间大小。常用单位代码：MTK表示平方米，FTK表示平方英尺，YDK表示平方码
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The size of the accommodation, e.g. in square meter or squarefoot.
Typical unit code(s): MTK for square meter, FTK for square foot, or YDK for square yard
_pRange.rdfs:label: floorSize

_pRange.descriptionZh: 车辆行驶特定距离或时间所消耗的燃料量（例如每100公里升）
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The amount of fuel consumed for traveling a particular distance or temporal duration with the given vehicle (e.g. liters per 100 km).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for liters per 100 km.  Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. L/100 km.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel consumption to another value.
_pRange.rdfs:label: fuelConsumption

_pRange.descriptionZh: 每单位燃料行驶的距离
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The distance traveled per unit of fuel used; most commonly miles per gallon (mpg) or kilometers per liter (km/L).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for miles per gallon or kilometers per liter. Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. mpg or km/L.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel economy to another value.
_pRange.rdfs:label: fuelEfficiency

_pRange.descriptionZh: 高度
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The height of the item.
_pRange.rdfs:label: height

_pRange.descriptionZh: 适用于金融产品的利率
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The interest rate, charged or paid, applicable to the financial product. Note: This is different from the calculated annualPercentageRate.
_pRange.rdfs:label: interestRate

_pRange.descriptionZh: 当前产品的库存量
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The current approximate inventory level for the item or items.
_pRange.rdfs:label: inventoryLevel

_pRange.descriptionZh: 贷款或信贷协议的期限。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The duration of the loan or credit agreement.
_pRange.rdfs:label: loanTerm

_pRange.descriptionZh: 由其里程表读取获得的一辆汽车自出厂以来所行驶的总里程
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The total distance travelled by the particular vehicle since its initial production, as read from its odometer.

Typical unit code(s): KMT for kilometers, SMI for statute miles
_pRange.rdfs:label: mileageFromOdometer

_pRange.descriptionZh: 住宿预定的成人人数
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The number of adults staying in the unit.
_pRange.rdfs:label: numAdults

_pRange.descriptionZh: 住宿预定的儿童人数
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The number of children staying in the unit.
_pRange.rdfs:label: numChildren

_pRange.descriptionZh: 车辆的轴数
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The number of axles.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfAxles

_pRange.descriptionZh: 车辆的车门数
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The number of doors.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfDoors

_pRange.descriptionZh: 组织的雇员数
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The number of employees in an organization e.g. business.
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfEmployees

_pRange.descriptionZh: 可用于汽车传动系统的前进档的总数
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The total number of forward gears available for the transmission system of the vehicle.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfForwardGears

_pRange.descriptionZh: 指明有多少人可以玩这个游戏（最少、最多或范围）
_pRange.rdfs:comment: Indicate how many people can play this game (minimum, maximum, or range).
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfPlayers

_pRange.descriptionZh: 这辆车的车主数量，包括现在的车主
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The number of owners of the vehicle, including the current one.

Typical unit code(s): C62
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfPreviousOwners

_pRange.descriptionZh: 住宿的房间数量
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The number of rooms (excluding bathrooms and closets) of the accommodation or lodging business.
Typical unit code(s): ROM for room or C62 for no unit. The type of room can be put in the unitText property of the QuantitativeValue.
_pRange.rdfs:label: numberOfRooms

_pRange.descriptionZh: 住宿允许的总入住人数（包括婴儿等）
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The allowed total occupancy for the accommodation in persons (including infants etc). For individual accommodations, this is not necessarily the legal maximum but defines the permitted usage as per the contractual agreement (e.g. a double room used by a single person).
Typical unit code(s): C62 for person
_pRange.rdfs:label: occupancy

_pRange.descriptionZh: 预约活动的参与人数
_pRange.rdfs:comment: Number of people the reservation should accommodate.
_pRange.rdfs:label: partySize

_pRange.descriptionZh: 菜谱的份量（例：多少人份，多少份量）
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The quantity produced by the recipe (for example, number of people served, number of servings, etc).
_pRange.rdfs:label: recipeYield

_pRange.descriptionZh: 报价对应的商品数量，例如 每4 kWh电1欧元，10块钱3个苹果。该属性适用于缺乏标准产品单价的产品。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The reference quantity for which a certain price applies, e.g. 1 EUR per 4 kWh of electricity. This property is a replacement for unitOfMeasurement for the advanced cases where the price does not relate to a standard unit.
_pRange.rdfs:label: referenceQuantity

_pRange.descriptionZh: 操作所需物料的数量
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The required quantity of the item(s).
_pRange.rdfs:label: requiredQuantity

_pRange.descriptionZh: 指向提供关于原始值的附加信息，例如： 参考温度。
_pRange.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
_pRange.rdfs:label: valueReference

_pRange.descriptionZh: 从实际的物理空间和法律规定的限制两方面的因素，可以容纳的的最多乘客人数。
_pRange.rdfs:comment:
The number of passengers that can be seated in the vehicle, both in terms of the physical space available, and in terms of limitations set by law.

Typical unit code(s): C62 for persons.
_pRange.rdfs:label: vehicleSeatingCapacity

_pRange.descriptionZh: 物体的重量
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The weight of the product or person.
_pRange.rdfs:label: weight

_pRange.descriptionZh: 物体的宽度
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The width of the item.
_pRange.rdfs:label: width

_pRange.descriptionZh: 业务的年度营业额
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The size of the business in annual revenue.
_pRange.rdfs:label: yearlyRevenue

_pRange.descriptionZh: 从创立到现在的运营年数
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The age of the business.
_pRange.rdfs:label: yearsInOperation

_pRange.descriptionZh: 操作所产出的结果
_pRange.rdfs:comment: The quantity that results by performing instructions. For example, a paper airplane, 10 personalized candles.
_pRange.rdfs:label: yield

_properties.descriptionZh: 表示实体附加特征的属性值对（例如cnschema.org中没有匹配属性的产品功能或其他特性）
_properties.rdfs:comment:
A property-value pair representing an additional characteristics of the entitity, e.g. a product feature or another characteristic for which there is no matching property in cnschema.org.

Note: Publishers should be aware that applications designed to use specific cnschema.org properties (e.g. http://cnschema.org/width, http://cnschema.org/color, http://cnschema.org/gtin13, ...) will typically expect such data to be provided using those properties, rather than using the generic property/value mechanism.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalProperty

_properties.rdfs:comment: The upper value of some characteristic or property.
_properties.rdfs:label: maxValue

_properties.rdfs:comment: The lower value of some characteristic or property.
_properties.rdfs:label: minValue

_properties.descriptionZh: 使用UN / CEFACT通用代码（3个字符）给出的测量单位或URL。 与UN / CEFACT通用代码相比，其他代码可能使用前缀后跟冒号。
_properties.rdfs:comment: The unit of measurement given using the UN/CEFACT Common Code (3 characters) or a URL. Other codes than the UN/CEFACT Common Code may be used with a prefix followed by a colon.
_properties.rdfs:label: unitCode

_properties.descriptionZh: 指示测量单位的字符串或文本。 如果您不能为unitCode提供标准单位代码，则很有用
_properties.rdfs:comment:
A string or text indicating the unit of measurement. Useful if you cannot provide a standard unit code for
unitCode.
_properties.rdfs:label: unitText

_properties.descriptionZh: 定量值或属性值节点的值。 对于定量值和货币金额，值的推荐类型是“数字”。 对于属性值，它可以是“Text”，“Number”，“Boolean”或“StructuredValue”。
_properties.rdfs:comment:
The value of the quantitative value or property value node.


For QuantitativeValue and MonetaryAmount, the recommended type for values is 'Number'.
For PropertyValue, it can be 'Text;', 'Number', 'Boolean', or 'StructuredValue'.
_properties.rdfs:label: value

_properties.descriptionZh: 指向提供关于原始值的附加信息，例如： 参考温度。
_properties.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
_properties.rdfs:label: valueReference

_pTree.descriptionZh: 定量地描述一个物品的属性，比如一个人的身高是185cm。
_pTree.rdfs:comment: A point value or interval for product characteristics and other purposes.
_pTree.rdfs:label: QuantitativeValue

_properties.descriptionZh: 该项的一个附加类型， 通常用于从外部词典中向微数据语法添加更加具体的类型。它表示事物和事物本身所属的类之间的关系。在RDFa语法中, 对多类型最好使用‘typeof’属性这样的本地RDFa语法. Schema.org 工具对额外类型的理解较弱，特别是外部定义的额外类型。
_properties.rdfs:comment: An additional type for the item, typically used for adding more specific types from external vocabularies in microdata syntax. This is a relationship between something and a class that the thing is in. In RDFa syntax, it is better to use the native RDFa syntax - the 'typeof' attribute - for multiple types. Schema.org tools may have only weaker understanding of extra types, in particular those defined externally.
_properties.rdfs:label: additionalType

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 表示实体附加特征的属性值对（例如cnschema.org中没有匹配属性的产品功能或其他特性）
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment:
A property-value pair representing an additional characteristics of the entitity, e.g. a product feature or another characteristic for which there is no matching property in cnschema.org.

Note: Publishers should be aware that applications designed to use specific cnschema.org properties (e.g. http://cnschema.org/width, http://cnschema.org/color, http://cnschema.org/gtin13, ...) will typically expect such data to be provided using those properties, rather than using the generic property/value mechanism.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: additionalProperty

isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The upper value of some characteristic or property.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: maxValue

isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The lower value of some characteristic or property.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: minValue

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 使用UN / CEFACT通用代码（3个字符）给出的测量单位或URL。 与UN / CEFACT通用代码相比，其他代码可能使用前缀后跟冒号。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: The unit of measurement given using the UN/CEFACT Common Code (3 characters) or a URL. Other codes than the UN/CEFACT Common Code may be used with a prefix followed by a colon.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: unitCode

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 指示测量单位的字符串或文本。 如果您不能为unitCode提供标准单位代码，则很有用
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment:
A string or text indicating the unit of measurement. Useful if you cannot provide a standard unit code for
unitCode.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: unitText

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 定量值或属性值节点的值。 对于定量值和货币金额，值的推荐类型是“数字”。 对于属性值，它可以是“Text”，“Number”，“Boolean”或“StructuredValue”。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment:
The value of the quantitative value or property value node.


For QuantitativeValue and MonetaryAmount, the recommended type for values is 'Number'.
For PropertyValue, it can be 'Text;', 'Number', 'Boolean', or 'StructuredValue'.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: value

isDomainOf.descriptionZh: 指向提供关于原始值的附加信息，例如： 参考温度。
isDomainOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
isDomainOf.rdfs:label: valueReference

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 预定资源需要提前的时间数（例如预定火车票需在发车前至少一小时）
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The amount of time that is required between accepting the offer and the actual usage of the resource or service.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: advanceBookingRequirement

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 借款（或投资产生的）年度利率，以单一百分比数表示，表示贷款期间实际的年度资金成本。这包括与交易相关的任何费用或额外费用。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The annual rate that is charged for borrowing (or made by investing), expressed as a single percentage number that represents the actual yearly cost of funds over the term of a loan. This includes any fees or additional costs associated with the transaction.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: annualPercentageRate

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 通常指汽车后备箱的容积
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The available volume for cargo or luggage. For automobiles, this is usually the trunk volume.

Typical unit code(s): LTR for liters, FTQ for cubic foot/feet

Note: You can use minValue and maxValue to indicate ranges.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: cargoVolume

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 就是指收到订单和货物离开仓库或准备取件（如果是上门取货的话）之间的延迟。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The typical delay between the receipt of the order and the goods either leaving the warehouse or being prepared for pickup, in case the delivery method is on site pickup.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: deliveryLeadTime

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 该项的深度。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The depth of the item.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: depth

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 保修期限。一般的单位代码是ANN表示年数，MON表示月数，DAY表示天数。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The duration of the warranty promise. Common unitCode values are ANN for year, MON for months, or DAY for days.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: durationOfWarranty

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 报价的有效时间，例如促销折扣仅限于某一周有效。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The duration for which the given offer is valid.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: eligibleDuration

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 报价最多可有购买多少货品，例如每客户最多可以购买一个优惠产品。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The interval and unit of measurement of ordering quantities for which the offer or price specification is valid. This allows e.g. specifying that a certain freight charge is valid only for a certain quantity.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: eligibleQuantity

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 房间大小。常用单位代码：MTK表示平方米，FTK表示平方英尺，YDK表示平方码
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The size of the accommodation, e.g. in square meter or squarefoot.
Typical unit code(s): MTK for square meter, FTK for square foot, or YDK for square yard
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: floorSize

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 车辆行驶特定距离或时间所消耗的燃料量（例如每100公里升）
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The amount of fuel consumed for traveling a particular distance or temporal duration with the given vehicle (e.g. liters per 100 km).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for liters per 100 km.  Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. L/100 km.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel consumption to another value.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: fuelConsumption

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 每单位燃料行驶的距离
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The distance traveled per unit of fuel used; most commonly miles per gallon (mpg) or kilometers per liter (km/L).


Note 1: There are unfortunately no standard unit codes for miles per gallon or kilometers per liter. Use unitText to indicate the unit of measurement, e.g. mpg or km/L.
Note 2: There are two ways of indicating the fuel consumption, fuelConsumption (e.g. 8 liters per 100 km) and fuelEfficiency (e.g. 30 miles per gallon). They are reciprocal.
Note 3: Often, the absolute value is useful only when related to driving speed ("at 80 km/h") or usage pattern ("city traffic"). You can use valueReference to link the value for the fuel economy to another value.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: fuelEfficiency

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 高度
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The height of the item.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: height

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 适用于金融产品的利率
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The interest rate, charged or paid, applicable to the financial product. Note: This is different from the calculated annualPercentageRate.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: interestRate

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 当前产品的库存量
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The current approximate inventory level for the item or items.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: inventoryLevel

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 贷款或信贷协议的期限。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The duration of the loan or credit agreement.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: loanTerm

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 由其里程表读取获得的一辆汽车自出厂以来所行驶的总里程
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The total distance travelled by the particular vehicle since its initial production, as read from its odometer.

Typical unit code(s): KMT for kilometers, SMI for statute miles
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: mileageFromOdometer

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 住宿预定的成人人数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The number of adults staying in the unit.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numAdults

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 住宿预定的儿童人数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The number of children staying in the unit.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numChildren

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 车辆的轴数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The number of axles.

Typical unit code(s): C62
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfAxles

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 车辆的车门数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The number of doors.

Typical unit code(s): C62
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfDoors

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 组织的雇员数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The number of employees in an organization e.g. business.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfEmployees

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 可用于汽车传动系统的前进档的总数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The total number of forward gears available for the transmission system of the vehicle.

Typical unit code(s): C62
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfForwardGears

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 指明有多少人可以玩这个游戏（最少、最多或范围）
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: Indicate how many people can play this game (minimum, maximum, or range).
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfPlayers

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 这辆车的车主数量，包括现在的车主
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The number of owners of the vehicle, including the current one.

Typical unit code(s): C62
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: numberOfPreviousOwners

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 住宿的房间数量
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:

Typical unit code(s): ROM for room or C62 for no unit. The type of room can be put in the unitText property of the QuantitativeValue.

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 住宿允许的总入住人数（包括婴儿等）
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The allowed total occupancy for the accommodation in persons (including infants etc). For individual accommodations, this is not necessarily the legal maximum but defines the permitted usage as per the contractual agreement (e.g. a double room used by a single person).
Typical unit code(s): C62 for person
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: occupancy

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 预约活动的参与人数
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: Number of people the reservation should accommodate.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: partySize

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 菜谱的份量（例：多少人份，多少份量）
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The quantity produced by the recipe (for example, number of people served, number of servings, etc).
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: recipeYield

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 报价对应的商品数量，例如 每4 kWh电1欧元，10块钱3个苹果。该属性适用于缺乏标准产品单价的产品。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The reference quantity for which a certain price applies, e.g. 1 EUR per 4 kWh of electricity. This property is a replacement for unitOfMeasurement for the advanced cases where the price does not relate to a standard unit.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: referenceQuantity

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 操作所需物料的数量
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The required quantity of the item(s).
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: requiredQuantity

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 指向提供关于原始值的附加信息，例如： 参考温度。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: A pointer to a secondary value that provides additional information on the original value, e.g. a reference temperature.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: valueReference

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 从实际的物理空间和法律规定的限制两方面的因素，可以容纳的的最多乘客人数。
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment:
The number of passengers that can be seated in the vehicle, both in terms of the physical space available, and in terms of limitations set by law.

Typical unit code(s): C62 for persons.
isRangeOf.rdfs:label: vehicleSeatingCapacity

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 物体的重量

isRangeOf.rdfs:label: weight

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 物体的宽度

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 业务的年度营业额

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 从创立到现在的运营年数

isRangeOf.descriptionZh: 操作所产出的结果
isRangeOf.rdfs:comment: The quantity that results by performing instructions. For example, a paper airplane, 10 personalized candles.

rdfs:comment: A point value or interval for product characteristics and other purposes.
rdfs:label: QuantitativeValue
